"name fields empty will log you in as anonymous. Note: we are planning to "
"rewrite this dialog window."
msgstr ""
"Sélectionnez <emphasis role=\"bold\"> <menuchoice> <guimenu>Outils</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Nouvelle connexion réseau</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> </"
